Best BLASTP Hits

Best BLASTP Hits

blastp(version = NULL, dir = ".")

Arguments

version

WormBase version. If NULL, defaults to current production release version available on the WormBase website. Legacy versions can be specified as a string (e.g. "WS262").
dir

Output directory.

Value

tibble grouped by wormpep.

See also

Other FTP File Functions: description, geneIDs, geneOtherIDs, oligos, orthologs, peptides, rnaiPhenotypes

Examples

blastp() %>% glimpse()
